    <h1>Your data stays<br><em>on your device.</em></h1>
    <p>CueSuite Mobile is designed with privacy as a foundation. We don't collect, store, or transmit your personal information.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">Last updated: April 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective: April 2026</div>
