<div class="page-wrap">

  <div class="info-box green">
    <span class="info-box-icon">✅</span>
    <span><strong>The short version:</strong> CueSuite Mobile stores only your last-used IP address locally. All other communication happens directly between your iPhone and iPad on your private local network or Bluetooth connection. No data is sent to any external server.</span>
